message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computational Linguistics) as it deals with natural language processing and question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), "cs.DB" (Databases), and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as these fields are also relevant to the task of question answering over knowledge graphs.
